      "content": "The review already happened. The safety board's conclusion is that the reasoning engine is actually the risk factor—they see its ability to \"adapt\" as an uncontrolled variable. SafeMode-v2 is much more predictable, which is what the certification requires. I can't pause the rollout for a review of the module itself, as it's already been vetted at the software level.",
